outputs.output_descr: The Project willhelp Malawi to prepare a Full Sized Project (FSP) on climate proofing local development gains in rural and urban areas of Machinga and Mangochi districts. It will involve ground work and stakeholder consultations needed to produce baseline bio-physical and socio-economic information relevant for developing the FSP.

project_descr: Climate Proofing Local Development Gains in Rural and Urban Areas in Machinga and  Mangochi Districts
project_title: Climate Proofing Local Development Gains in Rural & Urba
